程序包 Vue

类 InterfaceTable

java.lang.Object
Vue.InterfaceTable
所有已实现的接口:
Observer
public class InterfaceTable
extends java.lang.Object
implements Observer
The class InterfaceTable represents for the game table. It is a part of the design pattern Observer. It should be update according to the changes happened in the observable class, so it implements the class Observer.

If they have made their offer in their own window, The offers on the game table will be changes(one of them will be face-up). If their offer is taken, the offer will be replaced by a label "taken".
